Module kivakit.kernel
Package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.data.extraction

Interface Extractor<Value,​From>

Type Parameters:
Value - The value type
From - The object type
All Superinterfaces:
Broadcaster, NamedObject, Receiver, Transceiver, Transmitter
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseExtractor
public interface Extractor<Value,​From> extends Broadcaster
An extractor extracts a value from a source object of a given type.

Object Extraction

An extractor implements BaseExtractor.onExtract(Object) to extract a value from the source. In the following code, a Count is extracted from a PbfWay: 

 public class LaneCountExtractor extends BaseExtractor<Count, PbfWay>
 {
     public LaneCountExtractor( Listener listener)
     {
         super(listener);
         this(listener, "lanes");
     }

     public Count onExtract( PbfWay way)
     {
         Count laneCount;

             [...]

         return laneCount;
     }
 }

Usage of the extractor is then like this (where 'this' implements Repeater or Listener): 

 var lanes = new LaneCountExtractor(this).extract(way);
